    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "CLIPPER CALLING AT CATHAY\nFrom The Original Poster Painting\nby Paul George Lawler",
      "Hongkong, on the other side of the world-gateway to\none\nof the\nof call in the sixty-one\none\nhundred sixty-four ports\ncountries and colonies on Pan\nAmerican's Routes of the Flying\nClipper Ships-which\nlink the Three Americas with Europe, Australasia and\nthe Orient—largest air transport system in the world.\nPOST CARD\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nPRINTED IN U. S. A."
    ],
